result.execSummary:
The defendant Eric W. Phelps was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Eric W. Phelps is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Eric W. Phelps was found guilty of Battery [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse - Infliction of Physical Pain or Injury], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
